snippet.title: Patapon™ 2 Launch Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
The adventures of the brave Patapon™ tribe continue in the highly anticipated sequel to IGN's 2008 PSP® Game of the Year!  Patapon™ 2 is sure to satisfy fans of the original with double the content of the first, plus exciting new features.

Download Patapon™ 2 today on the PlayStation®Network!
